description.undefined: OWL ontology for the IFC conceptual data schema and exchange file format for Building Information Model (BIM) data. Release 4X3 ADD2.

abstract.value: This ifcOWL ontology is automatically generated from the EXPRESS schema 'IFC4X3_ADD2' using the 'IFCExpress2OWL' converter developed by Carlos Ramonell (carlos.ramonell@upc.edu). The ontology is identical to the ontology that is generated from the EXPRESS schema 'IFC4X3_ADD2.exp' using the 'IFC-to-RDF' converter developed by Pieter Pauwels (pipauwel.pauwels@ugent.be)
